<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.1">
<l>alampā veruṭṭāk koṉṟu tiriyu marakkarai</l>
<l>kulampāḻ paṭuttuk kulaviḷak kāyniṉ ṟakōṉmalai</l>
<l>cilampārk kavantu teyvamaka ḷirkaḷā ṭuñcīr</l>
<l>cilampā ṟupāyun teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of the king who stands as a lamp to [his] clan,</l>
<l rend="indent">having caused devastation to the clan of demons</l>
<l rend="indent">who wandered about terrifying and killing,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the South where flows the Cilampu river</l>
<l rend="indent">with the sound of dancing celestial ladies</l>
<l rend="indent">coming loudly from [their] tinkling anklets.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
